To install the dependencies:
  bundle install

Apply all migrations:
  bundle exec sequel -E -m migrations mysql2://dev:devpass@127.0.0.1/devdb

Rollback all migrations:
  bundle exec sequel -E -m migrations -M 0 mysql2://dev:devpass@127.0.0.1/devdb

For development and testing:
  docker-compose -f compose-for-development.yml up

To enter devconsole:
  DB_USER=dev DB_PASS=devpass DB_NAME=devdb DB_HOST=127.0.0.1 bundle exec ruby devconsole.rb

To run the specs:
  bundle exec rspec
